{"tid":1667641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真其實民陣搞流水式宗教集會可唔可行","createTime":"2019-10-21T14:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T14:19:17.000Z","uid":244387,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"638d6d2e2d2521fa41535191a31d496dc15d758a","tid":1667641,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"只要係民陣搞 點都實過百萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就覺得民陣可以搞個多元化宗教討論集會(可以諗個好啲嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 集會歡迎任何基督教 佛教 回教 伊斯蘭教 無宗教信仰人士...參與 不反對通知書都唔使申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過程絕對和理非 <br />\n而流水式我諗都唔需要多解釋 以'遊行'形式集會 好似818咁 雖然做法唔完美 但係我淨係諗到咁樣可以多啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對上一次過百萬已經係兩個月前818 我希望可以喺短期內搞一次凝聚一下大家嘅軍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝花時間睇我篇嘢  認同請推到俾民陣睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece08d60ace496fc2d397109c3e4b2d5344937f6","tid":1667641,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f91d5200ecf5a3f77a775368936ed16488b31244","tid":1667641,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a6b148ea78061d2919538748b6e097427dcef5a","tid":1667641,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b461bc80f0d28f9530fb03ad85cc4bf68d394f47","tid":1667641,"uid":244387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1c48546b7a6bd4875e2396e104602583f6d1ebc","tid":1667641,"uid":284304,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"係連登搞宗教共融只有死路一條<br />\n因為你地連基